    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a dependable choice for any driver. The engine starts up reliably and runs smoothly, while the transmission provides crisp, predictable shifts. On the exterior, the paint still holds a nice shine, though you will find some minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with normal use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with all major electronics and climate control systems functioning as intended. It is a solid, road-ready car that requires no immediate mechanical attention.",
