    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a solid, functional driver for someone willing to put in a little work. While the engine and transmission are operational, the car shows its age with some cosmetic blemishes, including minor paint fading and a few interior scuffs. There are some minor mechanical items that will need attention soon, such as aging suspension components and a slow oil leak, but it remains a reliable choice for daily commuting in its current state.",
